Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.governance

Class GovernanceDefinitionProperties

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.EntityProperties
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.OpenMetadataRootProperties
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.ReferenceableProperties
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.governance.GovernanceDefinitionProperties
Direct Known Subclasses:
GovernanceControlProperties, GovernanceDriverProperties, GovernancePolicyProperties, GovernanceStrategyProperties, RegulationProperties
public class GovernanceDefinitionProperties extends ReferenceableProperties
GovernanceDefinitionProperties provides the base class for many of the definitions that define the data strategy and governance program. It includes many of the common fields:
  • Document id
  • Title
  • Summary
  • Description
  • Scope
  • Domain identifier
  • Status
  • Priority
  • Implications
  • Outcomes
  • Results
  • AdditionalProperties
